Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.80,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(228.041,711.818)}Emperor Huán
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.15,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,Emperor Shāng of Hàn,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.51,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,Emperor Ān,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:26.84,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,Emperor Shùn,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:30.46,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,Emperor Chōng,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:34.55,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,Emperor Zhì,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.77,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,Emperor Huán and Emperor Líng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:43.22,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,Emperors' deposition became constant \Nand the court's power withered away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:46.66,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,With this, local gentry became despots, extorting the people
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:50.04,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,and annexing land as natural\Ndisasters ravaged the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:56.35,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,The common people were on a knife's edge, \Nliving in torment by desolation and starvation.
