Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}All shall prosper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:49.64,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(700.337,840.682)}The Yellow Turban Rebellion
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:48.51,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,Driven to the brink, the people could only rebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:54.28,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,Countless starving people rose high their flags, for one last, desperate push against fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:59.35,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,Finally in the first month of\Nthe seventh year of Guānghé,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:59.35,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: January 184 AD
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:02.80,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,the Yellow Turban Rebellion broke out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:06.38,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,They burned local government buildings,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:09.22,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,murdered officials, and occupied cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.90,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,War quickly broke out throughout the empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:14.86,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,Within ten days,\Nnews of the rebellion had spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:17.64,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,The empire was hurled into chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:24.44,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,440,6260,10740)\pos(212.536,693.409)}Hé Jìn\NStyled: Suìgāo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, the Yellow Turbans are powerful and the Imperial Army is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Permit the provinces to raise their own troops for defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:29.86,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(262.5,677.045)}Emperor Líng
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll leave it to you,\NGeneralissimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Appoint generals to levy troops\Nto suppress the rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:08:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}Administrator Liú Yān of Yōu Province\Nhereby announces to the public:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}"The Yellow Turbans have rebelled against His Majesty."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}"They are now invading\Nthe lands of Yōu Province,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}"causing harm and\Ncorrupting the common people."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}"Local guardsmen are ill-prepared and inadequate to defend the province."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}"With Heavens' mandate, His Majesty hath decreed:"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}"Recruit strong and loyal\Nmen from all four corners"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}"to reinforce the army\Nand protect the people."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:34.34,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(175.583,717.955)}Liú Bèi\NStyled: Xuándé
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:37.77,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1213.035,458.182)}Zhāng Fēi\NStyled: Yìdé
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a man, aren't you?\N The nation is in turmoil and all you do is sigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The market is open!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Butcher Zhāng?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Butcher Zhāng!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, coming, coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, I'm sorry. I'm afraid you\Nwon't be able to eat meat today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re here, aren’t you?\NCut me some meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I sell the meat\Nif my boss isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care. \NYou sell meat, I'll buy the meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the money, just give it!\NGo find Butcher Zhāng!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare not disturb him,\N you go find him yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so difficult about slaughtering a pig?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, this is your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why be afraid?\NJust sell the meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you sell it then.\NI can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The meat is in the well,\Nbut I can't get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not just move the millstone aside?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:09:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, move the millstone then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know my boss\Npromised earlier that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,whoever can move this millstone, can keep the meat inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it and the meat is yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't your boss going to lose his money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you can't move the millstone, then quit running your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the boss' business if there's money made or lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Good work, my friend! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, put it back in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir... powerful sir,\Nwhat will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the meat into small pieces.\NDistribute it to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Distribute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The meat belongs to me now.\NJust do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! I'll get right on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come one, everyone, get you some meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, this meat is on me. Take a piece, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go. Get me a piece, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You were here to buy meat\Nso you must pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If others can take\N some,why can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't take it anymore!\NPass me money, pass me money!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay! Sir, here's your payment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's there, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Fresh green beans, \Nwant to buy some?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What green beans?\NThis is clearly flour!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I sell fine products at a fair price.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing but flour!\NIt's nothing but flour!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you buying or milling?\NIf you're not buying, stop messing with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You get mad over a couple of beans!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you give away all my pork?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've come for a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.84,0:14:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one I want to hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:28.95,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If I want to make a name for myself,\Nwouldn't these two men be good companions?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:34.66,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's really extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:37.35,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This guy’s also a real man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You two heroes have excellent martial arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's admirable, really admirable!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I heard you lifted the millstone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so I came here to see you myself,\Nthat's what I was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I thought you came\Ndemanding money for the pork.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That little piece of pork?\NNot worth mentioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don’t you two come to my place for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about to rain.\NLet's take shelter at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Zhāng Fēi styled Yìdé!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:33.46,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Style names are given upon reaching adulthood. They're used as a form of respect between\Npeople of the same generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I love making friends with heroes from all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I'm lucky to meet two new heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It really puts me in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,After you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, come! After you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, bring wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Guān Yǔ, styled Yúnchǎng,\Nfrom Jiěliáng of Hédōng,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Liú Bèi, styled Xuándé.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We three met by chance but feel familiar straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit. Sit. Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:17:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've noticed you two are no ordinary men.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently the Yellow Turbans are running rampant.\NThe realm is in chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the time for heroes to rise. \NI wonder if you two heroes have a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, back in Jiěliáng,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tolerate a local despot oppressing the locals,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so in a fit of anger, I killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was forced to roam the jiānghú. It's been five or six years since the killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:24.11,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: The martial arts sub-culture that exist\Non the fringes of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I have many skills.\NI want to put them to use,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but in all my travels, I've found no opportunity to serve the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with killing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate that I haven't killed\Nall the villains in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the recruitment notice\Nat the city gate today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I intend to enlist in the army, to test my sword and meet destiny on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I die on the battlefield,\NI will die as a true and valiant man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what a man ought to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll enlist with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?\NWill you enlist with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s with the long sigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you implying that men\Nshouldn't help their country?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}Right now, it is a time of chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}heroes emerge in troubled times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}For heroes such as you two, \Nit is the time to show your valor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}But why must you subject\Nyourselves to serve others?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}These times will create heroes,\Nand those heroes will influence the times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}Now the Yellow Turbans are in rebellion\Nand the world has responded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}The court has ordered provinces to raise troops
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}because they are weak,\N with leaderless, feeble troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}Also, the eunuchs continue to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}Because of these things,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}there is bound to be\Nanother rebellion against tyranny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}When the Yellow Turban Rebellion is crushed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}the heroes of the times\Nwill surely rise up as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}Which hero will be the one\Nto hold power under heaven then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}No one knows for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing your speech is worth more\Nthan ten years of books!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's admirable, really admirable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m just a pig butcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's\Nhappening in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You just tell me what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so hesitant?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}There is a man who was\Noriginally a scion of the Hàn dynasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}His ancestor, Prince Jìng of Zhōngshān, was the 7th son of Emperor Xiàojǐng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}When his ancestor,\Nthe Marquis of Zhuōlù,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}failed to pay his annual\Ntribute to his ancestors,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.88,0:21:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}he was stripped of his rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}A branch of his family\Nheaded out to the countryside
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}and settled down in Lóusāng Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.48,0:21:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}Lóusāng Village? I know of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}There's a thousand-year-old\Nmulberry tree there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}The tree is tall and crowned.\NHence the name, Lóusāng Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:37.15,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Lóusāng literally means 'giant mulberry'
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}I also heard people saying\Nthe mulberry tree shelters a nobleman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}Yes, I'm familiar with this saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}However, for the last ten generations\N the descendants of this family
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}have been impoverished.\NThere's nothing but bare walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.91,0:22:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}As an imperial scion,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}why doesn't he restore\Nhis family's honor and rank?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}He began wandering at age 15, seeking teachers and making friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}He often thought of serving the state\Nand championing the people,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}but now he's 28 and has achieved nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.15,0:22:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}In the end, all his\Naspirations will be spent in vain,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.22,0:22:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}a heart full of tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.22,0:22:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.60,0:22:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the man before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.75,0:22:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say it earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:22:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That nobleman is right before me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:23:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Liú you say it,\Nand old Zhāng will do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.37,0:23:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.06,0:23:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to recruit local champions\Nand punish villains,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,only I don't have the resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to do something for the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.28,0:23:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I always speak the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.48,0:23:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.95,0:23:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.75,0:23:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A single thread cannot make a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.06,0:23:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A single tree doesn't make a forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.73,0:23:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm weak and can't do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.02,0:23:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't give up,\NI would gladly follow you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.76,0:23:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are like charcoal during a snowstorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:23:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too generous of you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.06,0:24:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi pays his respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.06,0:24:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.13,0:24:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Liú,\Nyou don't have to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.24,0:24:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanting to achieve great deeds,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.02,0:24:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wandered about half my life
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.37,0:24:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,searching for like-minded\Npeople, until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.51,0:24:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After washing away the sand,\NI've finally discovered gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.82,0:24:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Destiny has brought us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.27,0:24:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared to swear an oath of brotherhood\Nwith you two, sharing life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.26,0:24:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you two feel about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.06,0:24:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've also thought of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.31,0:24:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as we three share heart \Nand mind, clay can be changed to gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.55,0:24:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Together,You have me with you,\Nwe'll accomplish great deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.88,0:24:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I'm just a fighter,\NI understand honor and loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.71,0:25:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As the adage goes,\N"a good bird chooses a good tree to perch on,"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.20,0:25:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"and a good man chooses\Na worthy lord to serve."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.33,0:25:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My life's wish is fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.08,0:25:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, my life is tied to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.86,0:25:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My flesh is your flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.20,0:25:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fully committed!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.73,0:25:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.44,0:25:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear to go through thick and thin with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.84,0:25:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be your companion through life or death.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.64,0:25:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.24,0:25:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If my words are false,\Nmay heaven strike me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.95,0:25:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.75,0:25:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.82,0:25:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.77,0:25:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.44,0:25:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.75,0:25:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.93,0:25:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.56,0:25:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Though not born on the same day,\Nsame month or same year.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.62,0:25:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Though not born on the same day,\Nsame month or same year.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.78,0:26:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Though not born on the same day,\Nsame month or same year.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.78,0:26:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We seek to die on the same date,\Nsame month and same year.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.46,0:26:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We seek to die on the same date,\Nsame month and same year.
