Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.71,0:27:20.66,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,Life or death, never give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.95,0:27:29.44,Song,,0,0,0,,{\k81}tiān{\k42}dì {\k35}rì {\k45}yuè {\k106}zhuàng {\k116}wǒ {\k233}qíng{\k191}huái.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.95,0:27:29.44,Default Song version,,0,0,0,,Heaven and Earth, let my resolve\Nbe as strong as the Sun and Moon.
