Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.18,0:29:29.00,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1058.63,630)}Sūn Jiān\NStyled: Wéntái
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.58,0:29:39.45,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1151.74,683.636)}Cáo Cāo\NStyled: Mèngdé
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.78,0:30:40.30,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1171.731,737.501)}Dǒng Zhuó\NStyled: Zhòngyǐng
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.07,0:30:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you running, rebel!?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.92,0:31:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}Thank you, heroes, for saving me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.97,0:31:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}I'll remember it for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.77,0:31:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}May I ask what positions\Nyou three currently hold?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.70,0:31:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}We are commoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.80,0:31:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}Commoners?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.50,0:32:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother, you can't just...?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.80,0:32:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.15,0:32:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother, don't bother Elder Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.77,0:32:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You achieved so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.20,0:32:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,yet were rewarded with a\Nlowly magistrate post in Ānxǐ county.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.60,0:32:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That Sūn Jiān just curried favor\Nwith the higher-ups and was made a major.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.07,0:32:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.27,0:32:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That stinking imperial court,\Nit deserves its rebellions!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.12,0:32:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother, watch your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.27,0:33:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a commander of \Nthe imperial court, don't be rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.25,0:33:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about that Dǒng Zhuó! He did nothing, yet received a good magistrate position!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.50,0:33:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,By connecting with wealthy men
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.33,0:33:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and bribing the Ten Attendants,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.34,0:33:15.62,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: The Ten Attendants are the faction of eunuchs that control the Imperial Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.72,0:33:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That day on the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.87,0:33:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,remember what he was like? \NTrying to flee like a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.94,0:33:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.65,0:33:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was up to me,\NI'd kill him myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.00,0:33:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.74,0:33:49.30,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(263.923,540)\fade(255,0,255,0,500,4180,4540)}The County Inspector
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.30,0:33:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the new magistrate of this county?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.50,0:33:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.00,0:33:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.02,0:33:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.10,0:33:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Liú Bèi?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.60,0:33:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your background?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.48,0:34:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm descended from Emperor Xiàojǐng\Nthrough Prince Jìng of Zhōngshān.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.40,0:34:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're a scion of the Hàn dynasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.82,0:34:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.70,0:34:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me for lacking manners, my good sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.15,0:34:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.92,0:34:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're an imperial clansman,\Nplease do sit down, good sir. Let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.65,0:34:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.20,0:34:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.02,0:34:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,since you're an imperial scion, may I ask
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.87,0:34:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,why are you holding such a\Nlowly post as a county magistrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.15,0:34:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of my post, \NI'll do my best to help the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.75,0:34:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who recommended you to take this post, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.78,0:34:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I started recruiting within Zhuō commandery to suppress the Yellow Turbans.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.76,0:34:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been in more than thirty battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.77,0:34:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,For my humble merits,\NI was rewarded with this post.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.02,0:35:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to find a big tree\Nto lean on in the court,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.90,0:35:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,then you can lie low in the shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.52,0:35:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, it's fairly easy being a lowly official.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.00,0:35:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's harder for those higher on the ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.02,0:35:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever you want to do\N something, you need to pay up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.82,0:35:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an honest official, I've never committed any offense against the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.40,0:36:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the slightest offense?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.90,0:36:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.85,0:36:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare not deceive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.87,0:36:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're so confident\N Magistrate Liú, I'd still like to check into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.05,0:36:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.45,0:36:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the Inspector trouble you, Elder Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.67,0:36:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.05,0:36:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.35,0:36:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't ask for a bribe?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.45,0:36:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Not outright, but he was hinting at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.02,0:36:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I turned a deaf ear to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.97,0:36:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never exploit or mistreat the people. How could I afford to bribe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.22,0:36:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you had money, don't give it to him!\NWe'll see what he'll do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.87,0:36:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Magistrate Liú,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.88,0:36:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you're wanted by the Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.07,0:37:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What? The Inspector again?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.82,0:37:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned bureaucrat, merely a bully\Nleaning on the powerful. Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.25,0:37:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Inspector must be plotting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.77,0:37:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Best be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.45,0:37:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, the Inspector\Nmust be harboring evil intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.22,0:37:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.77,0:37:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng, Third Brother,\Nyou two wait for me at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.70,0:37:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.32,0:37:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.70,0:37:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.05,0:37:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.34,0:37:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your background?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.96,0:37:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm descended from Emperor Xiàojǐng through Prince Jìng of Zhōngshān.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.30,0:37:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Outrageous!\NYou dare pretend to be an imperial scion?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.10,0:37:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dare pretend!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.17,0:37:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare answer back?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.02,0:37:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get this post,\Nhow much did you pay in bribes?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.97,0:37:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Tell the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.10,0:38:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I started recruiting in Zhuō county to suppress the Yellow Turbans.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.06,0:38:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been in more than thirty battles. For my humble merits, I was rewarded with this post.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.60,0:38:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you lie about your feats!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.42,0:38:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I lied about nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.37,0:38:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my duty to clean up\Ncorrupt officials like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.77,0:38:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do investigate!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.47,0:38:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave now. If I find any wrongdoing, you'll be sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.80,0:38:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I take my leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.70,0:38:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This Liú Bèi is so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.45,0:38:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector, as the saying goes,\N"a thief bites down to the bone."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.51,0:38:40.80,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: This saying means that bad or wronged people will be vindictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.24,0:38:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Inspector announces\Na a hearing in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.07,0:38:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,During these three days, anyone\Nwho is dissatisfied with the magistrate,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.20,0:38:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,has experienced injustice, corruption, or has any evidence of crimes done against the people
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.20,0:38:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,will be the first to be heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.87,0:38:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Inspector will protect you.\NYou don't have to be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.90,0:39:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.50,0:39:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take revenge for the injustices done to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.92,0:39:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.45,0:39:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,since Magistrate Liú took office,\Nhe's committed no misdeeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.77,0:39:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He loves the common people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.72,0:39:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He has done no misdeeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.45,0:39:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's done nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.12,0:39:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he privately threaten you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.10,0:39:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like that, absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.50,0:39:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignorant peasants!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.12,0:39:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother, the Inspector is\Ndeliberately trying to frame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.90,0:39:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go beat him and run him\Nout of Ānxǐ county. It'll be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.40,0:39:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Third brother, don't be so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.91,0:39:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.40,0:39:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't beat him, can't even curse him!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.75,0:39:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.82,0:39:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.00,0:40:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.70,0:40:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.31,0:40:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.35,0:40:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.15,0:40:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,don't be reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.95,0:40:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.95,0:40:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.07,0:40:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going outside the city to ride my horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.45,0:40:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.75,0:40:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but only outside the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.95,0:40:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.40,0:40:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Magistrate Liú, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.47,0:40:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Zhāng, the Inspector has been\Nintimidating us to turn against Lord Liú.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.66,0:40:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Zhāng, we went to petition on behalf of Lord Liú,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.02,0:40:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Inspector wouldn't let us in\Nand he even beat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.65,0:41:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.10,0:41:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.04,0:41:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You bureaucrat cur, where's my Elder Brother!?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.95,0:41:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You bureaucrat cur!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.25,0:41:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.13,0:41:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.58,0:41:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You cur! I should beat you to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.12,0:41:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.72,0:41:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Xuándé, save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.97,0:41:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing this scumbag would be a good deed!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.33,0:41:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.06,0:41:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.40,0:41:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector, my Elder Brother\Nhas been nothing but dutiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.32,0:41:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's honest and cares for\Nthe people like his own children!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.65,0:41:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you try to harm him?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.35,0:41:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You only know how to steal money and ask for bribes!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.30,0:41:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly it's you who's the corrupt one!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.25,0:41:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My Elder Brother is innocent.\NWhere would he have the money for bribes?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.08,0:41:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}You sell positions and\Nconfiscate property on false charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.60,0:41:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}You deserve this punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.02,0:41:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Xuándé, sirs, sirs,\Nspare my life! Spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.07,0:42:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}Elder Brother, you've achieved so much on the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.88,0:42:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}yet only got to be a county magistrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.47,0:42:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}And now, you get slandered by this Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.85,0:42:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}This place is a thorn bush,\Nnot fit for a phoenix to perch on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.82,0:42:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714.526,906.136)}Better to kill him, resign this post,\Nthen head out for a new opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.57,0:42:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me! I'll never do it again!\NThose above forced me into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.95,0:42:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Subordinates follow their superiors!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.30,0:42:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector! You tried to frame the honest\Nand you tried to harm the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.62,0:42:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You deserve to be put down like a dog,\N but I will spare you this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.25,0:42:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your favor, Lord Xuándé!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.80,0:42:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My post...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.97,0:42:52.12,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Stamp seals represent government positions, and were required for decisions to be legal.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.45,0:42:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you may keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.42,0:43:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liú, please don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.47,0:43:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liú, please don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.20,0:43:28.38,Thinking,,0,0,0,,To avoid prosecution,\NLiú Bèi and his two brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.38,0:43:31.37,Thinking,,0,0,0,,became captains under Liú Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.05,0:43:35.06,Thinking,,0,0,0,,After Gōngsūn Zàn mentioned Liú's previous achievements,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.06,0:43:39.47,Thinking,,0,0,0,,he was promoted to major for the Píngyuán county magistrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.60,0:43:43.75,Thinking,,0,0,0,,There he gradually regrouped his old forces.
